Package com.iontrading.mkv

Class MkvEntitlementRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.iontrading.mkv.MkvEntitlementRequest
  • @Keep
@KeepPublicClassMemberNames
public final class MkvEntitlementRequest
extends Object
    This class represent a request for the entitlement server.

    An entitlement request is composed of three main elements:
    - user: the platform user for which the authorization is requested
    - a resource (service): this is composed by four different elements: the service type, the service name, the service container and the service object
    - a feature: it is actually composed as a string separated by / which identify the feature within a specific hierarchical tree

    See Also:
    MkvEntitlementManager
